[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{OK, you only have 4 HCP. But you have 10 cards in the Majors. And, you are in the balancing seat. If West is willing to let it die at 1NT your partner must have some strength. So you should use DONT. Youbid 2\H, showing both Major suits.

Partner responds 2\S.  

Partner prefers \Ss to \Hs. Since you were bare minimum you pass.}

